description: Industrial or commercial vacuum cleaner for your facility’s floors. Clean almost anywhere with Tennant Company's complete line of upright, back-pack and canister vacuum cleaners. Count on Tennant vacuuming equipment for durability and versatility for application in almost any environment with heavy-duty, lightweight, single motor, wet-dry options available.​​​​​​​ Deep-clean stains and odours in carpeting with Tennant heavy duty, deep-cleaning carpet extractors and remove surface stains and odours with interim carpet extractors. Tennant’s full line of carpet cleaning equipment gives you a variety of options and maximum flexibility to clean in large or small spaces. Our commercial carpet extractor designs include ride-ons, pull-back and forward-push designs.
name: Extractors, Vacuums, Floor Machines
